name: Spearit Bear - “9:10 AM (Instrumental Version)” Music NFT
description:
This NFT comes with a downloadable digital file of Spearit Bear's debut single "9:10 AM (Instrumental)" Purchase of this NFT transfers ownership of the digital file and image, not the right to ownership of the music itself. Commercial use of the image or the music file, aside from the resale of this NFT, must be requested and approved by Spearit Bear beforehand. This song was first released on streaming platforms in August of 2020 but is now exclusively available here.
The song 9:10 AM was written because Spearit Bear was struggling with believing in themself and pushing forward with music. 9:10 AM was the time that Spearit Bear was born and this song is meant to be a message to their younger self and others to follow their dreams no matter the struggles that come along the way.
This music NFT qualifies as one that can be collected to add to the 5 total needed for a collector to be considered a 'Distributor' and receive monthly Distributor pool payments from secondary sale royalties. More info at spearitbear.com/nfts
